summary:
I’m an Industrial Designer with previous studies in literature and a self-taught web developer with professional experience built since 2008, from 2013 onward I've worked focused on front-end technologies. I’m a technology enthusiast always in search for new and better tools and ways to build amazing digital products.

As team leader I’m empathic and objective, encouraging the team growth trough knowledge acquire and experimentation, convinced that communication is the key for a great team performance.
